NL-5632 XH  EINDHOVEN      FidoNet : 2:2802/123.1
The NETHERLANDS            AmigaNet: 39:150/101.1

Your ShareWare contribution will be gratefully accepted at the above
address also. 

I'd like to take the opportunity to thank Uli&Co for developing EGS,
and also Alexander Pratsch for his wonderful Dia program.  Of course
not forgetting Ing.Buro Helfrich for bringing us the Piccolo.  

I hope you guys/gals enjoy the program. Even the ones who don't find
it usefull enough to send in their contribution. 

@endnode Misc_Info
